.TH SPACEGL_SERVER.SH 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_server.sh \- SpaceGL galaxy server launcher script
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_server.sh
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_server.sh
is a Bash wrapper script that provides an interactive startup interface
for the SpaceGL galaxy server. It displays the SpaceGL banner, handles
master key authentication interactively when the
.B SPACEGL_KEY
environment variable is not already set, and then delegates execution
to
.BR spacegl_server (1).
.PP
All arguments passed to this script are forwarded verbatim to the
underlying
.B spacegl_server
binary.
.SH OPTIONS
Any option accepted by
.BR spacegl_server (1)
is passed through unchanged.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B SPACEGL_KEY
If set, the master key prompt is skipped and this value is used directly.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_server (1),
.BR spacegl_client.sh (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Nicola Taibi
